#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an5.43"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an5.43:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 5 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 5 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.43:0.2"
msgid "5. Muṇḍarājavagga "
msgstr "5. With King Muṇḍa "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: pañcaiṭṭhadhammasuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an5.43:0.3"
msgid "43. Iṭṭhasutta "
msgstr "43. Likable "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "an5.43:1.1"
msgid "Atha kho anāthapiṇḍiko gahapati yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ nisinnaṃ kho anāthapiṇḍikaṃ gahapatiṃ bhagavā etadavoca: "
msgstr "Then the householder Anāthapiṇḍika went up to the Buddha, bowed, and sat down to one side. The Buddha said to him: "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "an5.43:2.1"
msgid "“Pañcime, gahapati, dhammā iṭṭhā kantā manāpā dullabhā lokasmiṃ. "
msgstr "“Householder, these five things that are likable, desirable, and agreeable are hard to get in the world. "

msgctxt "an5.43:2.2"
msgid "Katame pañca? "
msgstr "What five? "

msgctxt "an5.43:2.3"
msgid "Āyu, gahapati, iṭṭho kanto manāpo dullabho lokasmiṃ; "
msgstr "Long life, "

msgctxt "an5.43:2.4"
msgid "vaṇṇo iṭṭho kanto manāpo dullabho lokasmiṃ; "
msgstr "beauty, "

msgctxt "an5.43:2.5"
msgid "sukhaṃ iṭṭhaṃ kantaṃ manāpaṃ dullabhaṃ lokasmiṃ; "
msgstr "happiness, "

msgctxt "an5.43:2.6"
msgid "yaso iṭṭho kanto manāpo dullabho lokasmiṃ; "
msgstr "fame, "

msgctxt "an5.43:2.7"
msgid "saggā iṭṭhā kantā manāpā dullabhā lokasmiṃ. "
msgstr "and heaven. "

msgctxt "an5.43:2.8"
msgid "Ime kho, gahapati, pañca dhammā iṭṭhā kantā manāpā dullabhā lokasmiṃ. "
msgstr "These are the five things that are likable, desirable, and agreeable, but hard to get in the world. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli3.48, sc3
#. VAR: patthanāhetu vā → na patthanahetu vā (s1-3, km) | na patthanāhetu vā (pts1)
msgctxt "an5.43:3.1"
msgid "Imesaṃ kho, gahapati, pañcannaṃ dhammānaṃ iṭṭhānaṃ kantānaṃ manāpānaṃ dullabhānaṃ lokasmiṃ na āyācanahetu vā patthanāhetu vā paṭilābhaṃ vadāmi. "
msgstr "And I say that these five things are not got by praying or wishing for them. "

msgctxt "an5.43:3.2"
msgid "Imesaṃ kho, gahapati, pañcannaṃ dhammānaṃ iṭṭhānaṃ kantānaṃ manāpānaṃ dullabhānaṃ lokasmiṃ āyācanahetu vā patthanāhetu vā paṭilābho abhavissa, ko idha kena hāyetha? "
msgstr "If they were, who would lack them? "

# NOTE: Accepting BB’s reading “vā pihetuṃ”.
#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc4
msgctxt "an5.43:4.1"
msgid "Na kho, gahapati, arahati ariyasāvako āyukāmo āyuṃ āyācituṃ vā abhinandituṃ vā āyussa vāpi hetu. "
msgstr "A noble disciple who wants to live long ought not pray for it, or hope for it, or pine for it. "

msgctxt "an5.43:4.2"
msgid "Āyukāmena, gahapati, ariyasāvakena āyusaṃvattanikā paṭipadā paṭipajjitabbā. "
msgstr "Instead, they should practice the way that leads to long life. "

msgctxt "an5.43:4.3"
msgid "Āyusaṃvattanikā hissa paṭipadā paṭipannā āyupaṭilābhāya saṃvattati. "
msgstr "For by practicing that way they gain long life "

msgctxt "an5.43:4.4"
msgid "So lābhī hoti āyussa dibbassa vā mānusassa vā. "
msgstr "as a god or a human being. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc5
msgctxt "an5.43:5.1"
msgid "Na kho, gahapati, arahati ariyasāvako vaṇṇakāmo vaṇṇaṃ āyācituṃ vā abhinandituṃ vā vaṇṇassa vāpi hetu. "
msgstr "A noble disciple who wants to be beautiful ought not pray for it, or hope for it, or pine for it. "

msgctxt "an5.43:5.2"
msgid "Vaṇṇakāmena, gahapati, ariyasāvakena vaṇṇasaṃvattanikā paṭipadā paṭipajjitabbā. "
msgstr "Instead, they should practice the way that leads to beauty. "

msgctxt "an5.43:5.3"
msgid "Vaṇṇasaṃvattanikā hissa paṭipadā paṭipannā vaṇṇapaṭilābhāya saṃvattati. "
msgstr "For by practicing that way they gain beauty "

msgctxt "an5.43:5.4"
msgid "So lābhī hoti vaṇṇassa dibbassa vā mānusassa vā. "
msgstr "as a god or a human being. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc6
msgctxt "an5.43:6.1"
msgid "Na kho, gahapati, arahati ariyasāvako sukhakāmo sukhaṃ āyācituṃ vā abhinandituṃ vā sukhassa vāpi hetu. "
msgstr "A noble disciple who wants to be happy ought not pray for it, or hope for it, or pine for it. "

msgctxt "an5.43:6.2"
msgid "Sukhakāmena, gahapati, ariyasāvakena sukhasaṃvattanikā paṭipadā paṭipajjitabbā. "
msgstr "Instead, they should practice the way that leads to happiness. "

msgctxt "an5.43:6.3"
msgid "Sukhasaṃvattanikā hissa paṭipadā paṭipannā sukhapaṭilābhāya saṃvattati. "
msgstr "For by practicing that way they gain happiness "

msgctxt "an5.43:6.4"
msgid "So lābhī hoti sukhassa dibbassa vā mānusassa vā. "
msgstr "as a god or a human being. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc7
msgctxt "an5.43:7.1"
msgid "Na kho, gahapati, arahati ariyasāvako yasakāmo yasaṃ āyācituṃ vā abhinandituṃ vā yasassa vāpi hetu. "
msgstr "A noble disciple who wants to be famous ought not pray for it, or hope for it, or pine for it. "

msgctxt "an5.43:7.2"
msgid "Yasakāmena, gahapati, ariyasāvakena yasasaṃvattanikā paṭipadā paṭipajjitabbā. "
msgstr "Instead, they should practice the way that leads to fame. "

msgctxt "an5.43:7.3"
msgid "Yasasaṃvattanikā hissa paṭipadā paṭipannā yasapaṭilābhāya saṃvattati. "
msgstr "For by practicing that way they gain fame "

msgctxt "an5.43:7.4"
msgid "So lābhī hoti yasassa dibbassa vā mānusassa vā. "
msgstr "as a god or a human being. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc8
msgctxt "an5.43:8.1"
msgid "Na kho, gahapati, arahati ariyasāvako saggakāmo saggaṃ āyācituṃ vā abhinandituṃ vā saggānaṃ vāpi hetu. "
msgstr "A noble disciple who wants to go to heaven ought not pray for it, or hope for it, or pine for it. "

msgctxt "an5.43:8.2"
msgid "Saggakāmena, gahapati, ariyasāvakena saggasaṃvattanikā paṭipadā paṭipajjitabbā. "
msgstr "Instead, they should practice the way that leads to heaven. "

msgctxt "an5.43:8.3"
msgid "Saggasaṃvattanikā hissa paṭipadā paṭipannā saggapaṭilābhāya saṃvattati. "
msgstr "For by practicing that way they gain heaven, "

msgctxt "an5.43:8.4"
msgid "So lābhī hoti saggānanti. "
msgstr "they are one who gains the heavens. "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: sc9
msgctxt "an5.43:9.1"
msgid "Āyuṃ vaṇṇaṃ yasaṃ kittiṃ, "
msgstr "For one who desires a continuous flow "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an5.43:9.2"
msgid "Saggaṃ uccākulīnataṃ; "
msgstr "of exceptional delights—"

#. HTML: <br>
#. VAR: patthayānena → patthayamānena (mr)
msgctxt "an5.43:9.3"
msgid "Ratiyo patthayānena, "
msgstr "long life, beauty, fame and reputation, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an5.43:9.4"
msgid "Uḷārā aparāparā. "
msgstr "heaven, and birth in an eminent family—"

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli3.49, sc10
msgctxt "an5.43:10.1"
msgid "Appamādaṃ pasaṃsanti, "
msgstr "the astute praise diligence "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an5.43:10.2"
msgid "puññakiriyāsu paṇḍitā; "
msgstr "in making merit. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an5.43:10.3"
msgid "Appamatto ubho atthe, "
msgstr "Being diligent, an astute person "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an5.43:10.4"
msgid "adhigaṇhāti paṇḍito. "
msgstr "secures both benefits: "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc11
#. VAR: Diṭṭhe dhamme ca → diṭṭheva dhamme (bj)
msgctxt "an5.43:11.1"
msgid "Diṭṭhe dhamme ca yo attho, "
msgstr "the benefit in this life, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an5.43:11.2"
msgid "yo cattho samparāyiko; "
msgstr "and in lives to come. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an5.43:11.3"
msgid "Atthābhisamayā dhīro, "
msgstr "A wise one, comprehending the meaning, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an5.43:11.4"
msgid "paṇḍitoti pavuccatī”ti. "
msgstr "is called ‘astute’.” "

#. HTML: </p></blockquote><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an5.43:11.5"
msgid "Tatiyaṃ. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
